dataset_description.json.Name: Pilot data for Loneliness in the Brain: Distinguishing Between Hypersensitivity and Hyperalertness

diagnosis.Description: History of diagnosis of mental health condition.

task-roddball_eeg.json.TaskDescription: Roving oddball task with face stimuli with either happy, angry, or neutral facial expression. To keep participants engaged, 10% of trials contained a red fixation cross. Participants were instructed to press the space bar when they noticed the red cross.
